                <mxCell id="legend_text" value="• Yellow box: host gateway boundary — owns HTTP, auth, routing, observability.&#xa;• Purple box: WASM runtime — sandboxed; deterministic.&#xa;• Green box: noodle-detect.wasm artifact — pure function from (req, resp, ctx) → AttributionFacts (ADR 039 §2.3).&#xa;• Dashed arrow: in-process call across the WASM boundary via extern &quot;C&quot; shim (ADR 039 §2.5).&#xa;• Host telemetry consumer is the host&#39;s responsibility; AttributionFacts is the contract between the two." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
